Arsenal beat Burnley 1-0 in the Premier League on Saturday was their eighth win in a row . 
  Aaron Ramsey scored the only goal of the game in the 12th minute . 
  The Gunners face Chelsea in their next league game at the Emirates . 
  Olivier Giroud wants Arsenal to continue their winning streak . 
  The win was Arsenal's best since the Invincibles in 2004 . 
 